title: Sweet Potato Bake
ingredients: ["2 to 2 1/2 lb. sweet potatoes", "1/4 c. oleo, melted", "1/4 to 1/2 c. sugar", "1/4 c. raisins", "1/2 c. chopped nuts", "1/3 c. miniature marshmallows"]
directions: ["Cook sweet potatoes to just tender, about 30 minutes.", "Drain, cool and peel.", "In large bowl, mash potatoes.", "Stir in oleo, sugar and raisins."]

title: Steak(Crisp And Crusty)
ingredients: ["1 (2.8 oz.) can French-fried onions, coarsely crumbled", "2 Tbsp. olive oil", "2 tsp. spicy brown mustard", "4 thinly sliced beef top round steaks (about 1 lb.)"]
directions: ["Put broiler pan 8 to 10-inches from heat and preheat broiler. In a shallow bowl, combine oil and mustard. Dip steaks into mixture, then into the onions, coating completely. Place steaks on a rimmed baking sheet and broil for 3 to 4 minutes on each side."]
